highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Tears” is the highest at #4.
“The Dead Dance” by Lady Gaga is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #29.
“Blinding Lights” by The Weeknd has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 302 weeks straight.
“Qué Pasaría...” by Rauw Alejandro and Bad Bunny is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 43 spots at #123.
